libpocsag (1.1.0-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Add FSK modulator and demodulator for full audio pipeline
  * Add baseband NRZ output for FM transmitter / multimon-ng use
  * Fix POCSAG numeric BCD encoding
  * Support sample rates: 8000, 16000, 32000, 48000 Hz
  * Support baud rates: 512, 1200, 2400
  * Frequency validation and per-instance thread safety documented
  * 63 tests, valgrind clean, zero allocation

